data.description: Gorgeous and practically brand new 5BR/3BA 3,145 Sq. Ft. Hughston Home Cypress Floor Plan less than a year old which won't last long in The Mossy Meadows Community and in the popular HOCO High School District. Conveniently located to RAFB, Rigby's Water Park, IMAX movie theater, easy I-75 access, shopping, schools, restaurants, and MUCH MORE!!! Granite countertops in kitchen and engineered hardwood floors in living areas. Coffered ceiling in formal dining room and great room, hardwood stairs and open rod iron railings. Gorgeous 'Open Floor Plan Concept', spacious Owner's Suite, tiled shower and over-sized garden tub great for soaking. Covered and screened back GameDay Porch with fireplace and speakers and a large homesite that's spacious enough to accommodate a swimming pool. Spacious driveway for parking and side-entry two car garage with just too many amenities and features to name!!! Don't miss out on this beautiful home in which it WON'T LAST LONG!!! Make your appointment today!!!
